'''''Fiela's Child''''' ni ikinamico yo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]] yanditswe na Dalene Matthee kandi yasohotse mu 1985. Igitabo cyanditswe mbere muri [[Ikinyafurikansi|Afrikaans]] ku izina rya '''''Fiela se Kind''''', nyuma kiza guhindurwa mu [[Icyongereza|Cyongereza]], [[Igifaransa]], [[Ikidage]], [[Icyesipanyole|Icyesipanyoli]], igitaliyani, Igiheburayo, Isilande na Sinhalese, n'ibindi.

== Insanganyamatsiko ==
Matthee akemura ibibazo by’ibidukikije, insanganyamatsiko zishingiye ku ivanguramoko no kuvangura amoko. blue-buck burenze guhigwa kandi inzovu ziricwa . Umubano hagati y'abazungu nabandi birabura uragoye. Nubwo ibi mbere ya Apartheid mugihe tekiniki habaye uburinganire imbere y amategeko, gahunda y'amategeko yabogamye kandi ishyigikira abazungu. Inganda zo mu nyanja zibabajwe no kwinjiza amato akoreshwa na parike.

== Ibice byo kugarukira ==
Mu gitabo cyanditswe na Dalene Matthee icyerekezo cyo kugarukira, aho umuntu abasha guhitamo uwo ari we n'icyo agomba kuba afite, uruhare runini. Mu gitabo, Benjamini ari mu ntera ntarengwa kandi ntazi umwirondoro we. Na none, igenamiterere risobanurwa ko riri murwego ntarengwa bityo bibera kumpande zombi z'umusozi  .

== Filime ==
Igitabo cyakozwe muri firime mu 1988 gikinwamo Shaleen Surtie-Richards nka Fiela. <ref>[https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0144200/maindetails Fiela se Kind (1988)]</ref> Filime muri 2019 yakinnye na Zenobia Kloppers nka Fiela.
